	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />thanks, guys!<br /><br />We reserved some space for a status bar which we never got to implement.<br />As for the top border, I guess that was a questionable decision. I figured it would be bad if the top rows were cut off by overscan with how we were designing maps at first.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
